node.text: “Leaving a Legacy is extremely important to me with this brand. The reason I started it was to bring a community together of different types of women from all around the world. That’s what Tribe means in 12th Tribe. It’s a family and like-minded community of all different types of people that come together under one mission.” -@demimarchese

node.title: WHAT DOES IT MEAN TO LEAVE YOUR LEGACY?

node.text: “When you die, you don’t get to bring anything with you. Leaving a legacy is super important to me. We want to create life value for everyone. We want people to have Cuts on their resume to say, ‘Damn, they worked at Cuts.’ And to do that, it takes trailblazing and doing things that are harder and against the norm. That’s all part of building a legacy.” - @stevenborrelli  #LeaveYourLegacy

node.title: WHAT DOES IT MEAN TO LEAVE YOUR LEGACY?

NEW. The Raptor Collection is dressed to kill with a bold sport chronograph dial and a lifted, bolted bezel. #MVMTRaptor
Which is your favorite? (Left to right)

2.	Dark Star
3.	Sunflare Gold
